DESCRIPTION:Pawsitively Giving Day Pet Donation Drive & Community Photo Mom
	ent Thursday\, March 19\, 2026 11:00 AM – End of Day Cogir of Kirkland inv
	ites residents\, families\, and community partners to join us for Pawsitiv
	ely Giving Day\, a special pet donation drive supporting a local rescue or
	ganization. Guests are encouraged to bring new or gently used pet items\, 
	including blankets\, leashes\, collars\, toys\, and other pet supplies. Wh
	ile you’re here\, stop by our branded photo area to capture a moment and s
	hare your support for animals in need. Together\, we’re giving back to our
	 community—one donation at a time. Please RSVP by March 15\, 2026 Contact:
	 Donna Garee Email: Donna.Garee@CogirUSA.com For more information\, call 4
	25-546-0574.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pawsitively-
	giving-day/18291008/2026-03-19T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
