SUMMARY:Best Day Ever: South Park
DTSTAMP:20260315T172900Z
DTSTART:20260321T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our first Best Day Ever event with Cultivate South 
	Park! This exciting one-day event will feature activities like West Africa
	n dance & storytelling\, chocolate tasting\, Duwamish River tours\, local 
	food tasting\, arts & crafts\, and more. Sign up now for a full day of joy
	 and community!\n\nBest Day Ever is a one-day\, community-powered experien
	ce that celebrates the vibrancy\, culture\, and pride of Seattle’s neighbo
	rhoods. Co-created by the Department of Neighborhoods \\(DON\\) and the Se
	attle Chamber of Connection \\(SCoC\\)\, Best Day Ever strengthens civic b
	elonging by bringing people\, place\, and purpose together. Guided by DON’
	s Community Engagement Framework and the Chamber’s Six Points of Connectio
	n\, this initiative uplifts community leadership and honors the histories\
	, creativity\, and cultural assets that make each neighborhood unique.\n\n
	A thriving neighborhood is one where residents feel connected\, represente
	d\, and proud of where they live — and Best Day Ever is designed to bring 
	that feeling to life. Each activation builds belonging through service\, s
	torytelling\, movement\, shared meals\, joyful connection\, and economic v
	isibility for local small businesses.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/even
	ts/#/details/best-day-ever-south-park/18210712/2026-03-21T00\n\nFrom SEAto
	day - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/best-day-ever-south-park/
	18210712/2026-03-21T00
LOCATION:South Park Hall\, 1253 S Cloverdale St.\, Seattle\, WA
