	pm\n\nDescription\n\nCombining gorgeous anime-inspired artwork with the be
	st of Western card game design\, Grand Archive features innovative gamepla
	y and a unique resource system. Choose your element\, pick from over a doz
	en different champions\, and build your deck from powerful allies\, spells
	\, and weapons.\n\nJoin the Seattle community for competitive and fun week
	ly events \\(with prizing\\) and discover for yourself why this is the hot
	test new TCG around!\n\nContact Wild Shiba on the Tabletop Village Discord
	 for more information and registration.\n\nMORE INFO \\+ REGISTRATION\n\nh
	ttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/grand-archive-weekly-tourname
